text: Americans in more than 1,900 counties saw increased levels of clustering during Thanksgiving travel, compared to the previous week, according to cellphone location data. https://t.co/Q69zzj677B

name: NBCNews
text:
California Gov. Newsom introduces new regional stay-at-home order on Thursday.

The order will require bars, wineries, hair salons and other nonessential businesses across 5 areas to close for 3 weeks once the region’s ICU capacity falls below 15%. https://t.co/fXRT9Ctlr5

name: NBCNews
text:
Election officials investigate actions of a Florida lawyer who they say tried to register to vote in Georgia runoff.

Moving to Georgia just to vote — with no intention of staying in the state afterward — can amount to a felony, Georgia Sec. of State says. https://t.co/ldBneKv50Z

text: More than 25 PPP loans worth more than $3.65M were given to businesses with addresses at Trump and Kushner real estate properties, paying rent to those owners, according to an NBC News analysis. https://t.co/s2tA4O9hWo
